title: The Tina Challenge: The Final Day
description: It's the Final Day of The Tina Challenge and Tina is granting double points since we missed yesterday.  We go head to head in a Rap Battle and whoever loses is going to have to do The Tina Challenge!  So we finally find out what's in the box and the loser has to do THE TINA CHALLENGE.
